description: Channing has been a big fan of Maskurbate for many years now. He wrote me about meeting his favorite pornstar, Manuel Deboxer. He was lucky that Manuel was in town so I was able to arrange a meeting, as long as I was authorized to shoot the entire thing. I could tell that Channing has never done porn before and was very nervous & excited to share a scene with his idol. He had trouble keeping his hands and mouth off Deboxer as my camera was sometimes in the way. Reality at its best!
title: MSKB Fan meets Deboxer, Scene #01
